Present Simple Question  -- sub + don't/doesn't + v1
-----------------------
 
I/we/they/you  -- don't
he/she/it      -- doesn't

ex:     I don't drink coffee
	We don't watch television very often
	Siva doesn't do his job very well
	Paula doesn't usually have breakfast
	Jyothi speaks Telugu and she doesn't speak Hindi
	I never go to theatre
